content: Hey, I'm looking for some home decor inspiration. I recently got a set of ceramic planters from Target and I'm thinking of rearranging my living room. Do you have any suggestions on how to style them? By the way, I've been trying to be more eco-friendly and I've started shopping at thrift stores more often - I also bought a like-new pair of skinny jeans for $12 at Goodwill last month, such a great deal!
